Title: Meld for OSX by yousseb
Description: Homepage for Meld macOS port. Meld is a visual diff and merge tool targeted at developers. Meld helps you compare files, directories, and version controlled projects. It provides two- and three-way comparison of both files and directories, and has support for many popular version control systems such as git, mercurial and others.
